      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Readers called our slice-of-battlefield-life gripping and found much to commend in the behavior of the soldiers. Others foresaw glitches in wars waged with unmanned missiles. And there was more tough talk for the out-of-work execs whose self-esteem seemed overly invested in their incomes.</p>
